        "rating": 1,
        "text": "I walked into the establishment, it smelled it was crowded , and the person who was running it was taking his time with a person trying to sell or pawn stuff. Person asked me what I wanted I told him then he said oh I have some of those, and turned to help the two homeless people that were still pulling stuff out of her bag. Hope there sales were worth it because you have lost my business.",
