        "rating": 5,
        "text": "Ace Pawn Shop is a hidden jewel here in our own back yard. To elaborate on the point it has a great variety of electronics to choose from as well as many other items. The staff is always friendly and helpful. It's nice to know that I can come here and find what I need without having to pay a price just to come in like the flee market. I will be coming back to do business with them again soon!",
